## 4. In-App Purchases

Hydrio offers an optional **Hydrio Premium** subscription that unlocks:

- Advanced hydration insights
- Unlimited drink types
- Smart reminders
- Full achievements system

### Purchase Details
- **Price:** $9.99 for life time access with a one time purchase
- All transactions are processed exclusively by **Apple** via the App Store
- We do **not** receive, store, or have access to your payment information
- Purchases are subject to [Apple's Terms of Sale](https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/)

### Refunds
Refund requests must be submitted directly to Apple at [reportaproblem.apple.com](https://reportaproblem.apple.com). We are unable to process refunds directly.

### Subscription Management
You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time via:  
**iOS Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions → Hydrio**

