## 5. Children's Privacy

Hydrio does not knowingly collect any personal data from anyone, including children under 13. Since all data is stored locally on your device and never transmitted, the app is safe for all ages.

---

## 6. Data Security

Your data is protected by your device's built-in security:

- Face ID / Touch ID / device passcode
- iOS data protection APIs
- App sandboxing (your data is inaccessible to other apps)

We recommend keeping your iOS version up to date to benefit from Apple's latest security improvements.

---

## 7. Deleting Your Data

You have full control over your data at all times:

**Option 1 — Reset within the app:**  
Hydrio → Settings → Data → **Reset All Data**

**Option 2 — Uninstall the app:**  
Deleting Hydrio from your device permanently removes all locally stored data.

There is no account to delete and no server-side data to request removal of.

---

## 8. Third-Party Services

Hydrio does not integrate with any third-party analytics, advertising, or data platforms. The only third-party involvement is **Apple**, which handles:

- App distribution (App Store)
- In-App Purchase processing
- Local notification delivery

All of the above are governed by [Apple's Privacy Policy](https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/).

